```plantuml
@startuml hyper-prog_hasses

actor WebServer
actor Client
participant "hasses Server" as Hasses
participant "Epoll Mechanism" as Epoll
database "Client Data" as CData

activate WebServer
activate Hasses

WebServer -> Hasses: Connect via FIFO/TCP
Hasses -> Epoll: Register connection

loop Handle incoming connections
    Client -> Hasses: SSE Handshake Request
    activate Client
    Hasses -> Epoll: Monitor client readiness
    Hasses -> CData: Add client to data structure
    activate CData
    CData -> Hasses: Acknowledge client addition
    deactivate CData

    Hasses -> Client: Send SSE Handshake Response
    activate Epoll
    Client -> Epoll: Ready for events
    deactivate Client
    deactivate Epoll
end

loop Message Routing
    WebServer -> Hasses: Send message
    Hasses -> CData: Retrieve subscribed clients
    activate CData
    CData -> Hasses: Return client list
    deactivate CData

    Hasses -> Epoll: Notify client readiness
    activate Client
    Hasses -> Client: Deliver message
    deactivate Client
end

WebServer -> Hasses: Query server status
Hasses -> WebServer: Return status information

Hasses -> WebServer: Disconnect
deactivate Hasses
deactivate WebServer

@enduml
```